headline: Arthur J. Gallagher (NYSE:AJG) Joins Forces With New Zealand Rugby In Landmark Partnership
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher (NYSE:AJG) recently announced a landmark partnership with New Zealand Rugby, becoming the official insurance broker with branding presence on national team's shorts. Over the past month, the company's share price increased by 4%, aligning with overall positive market growth trends, albeit slightly above the market's longer-term 13% increase over the past year. This partnership and similar strategic moves, alongside the appointment of Ian Picton as head of Energy...

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Wilkins & Associates Insurance Services, Inc.
